<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.buddhadharma.org/EightVerses" class="external text" title="http://www.buddhadharma.org/EightVerses" rel="nofollow">Langri Tangpa's Eight Verses for Training the Mind</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <i>Universal Compassion: Inspiring Solutions for Difficult Times</i>, pages 5-6, Tharpa Publications (4th. ed., 2002) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780948006722" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-948006-72-2</a></li>
