<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://lojongmindtraining.com/sectionSummary.aspx?sectionID=0" class="external text" title="http://lojongmindtraining.com/sectionSummary.aspx?sectionID=0" rel="nofollow">Tonglen and Mind Training Site</a></li>
</ol>
